Title: subtractNanoseconds
Description: Subtracts a specified number of nanoseconds from a date with time or a string-encoded date with time.
date_time: Date with time to subtract specified number of nanoseconds from. DateTime/DateTime64, String.num: Number of nanoseconds to subtract. (U)Int*, Float*.
Returns date_time minus num nanoseconds. DateTime64.
Examples: WITH    toDateTime('2024-01-01 00:00:00') AS date_time,    '2024-01-01 00:00:00' AS date_time_stringSELECT    subtractNanoseconds(date_time, 1000) AS subtract_nanoseconds_with_date_time,    subtractNanoseconds(date_time_string, 1000) AS subtract_nanoseconds_with_date_time_string
